e notion of heritage language learner as a site of negotiation regarding the legitimate knowledge of language and ways of belonging, while offering practical suggestions for schools.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aJapanese languagexStudy and teachingxForeign speakers. 0aLanguage and languagesxStudy and teachingzUnited States. 0aLanguage teachersxTraining ofzUnited States. 0aSecond language acquisition. 4aJapanisch. 4aSoziolinguistik. 4aSpracherwerb. 4aSprachförderung. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aHeritage Language School.  aJapanese.  aLanguage Education.  aSociolinguistics.  aSubjectivity.1 aLee, Kiri, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)z978311023845708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015z978311074296108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LINGUISTICS 2013z978311031724408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK 2013z9783110317237oZDB-23-DSP0 cprintz978161451399540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161451283740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781614512837423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781614512837/original  a978-3-11-023845-7  DGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlis